OL,3,CTeachers reject pay offer for second
OL,4,Ctime
OL,6,FThe majority of teachers in Northern
OL,7,FIreland have again rejected a proposed
OL,8,Fdeal to resolve a pay dispute.
OL,10,FThe Northern Ireland Teachers'
OL,11,FCouncil, which represents the teaching
OL,12,Funions in negotiations with
OL,13,Fmanagement, said members were still
OL,14,Fnot prepared to accept the 5.5% uplift
OL,15,Foffer.
OL,17,FTeachers rejected an initial offer in
OL,18,FFebruary ` a move that appeared less
OL,19,Fabout the proposed pay rise and more
OL,20,Fabout concerns over workload.
