OL,6,FA new offer was tabled by the
OL,7,Fmanagement side of negotiations last
OL,8,Fweek that included what was described
OL,9,Fas an enhanced package of commitments
OL,10,Faround reducing workload.
OL,12,FDespite that, teachers have again
OL,13,Frejected the proposed package.
OL,15,FTeachers have been engaging in
OL,16,Findustrial action short of strike
OL,17,Fduring the pay dispute.
