OL,6,FJacquie White, Ulster Teachers' Union
OL,7,Fgeneral secretary and chair of the
OL,8,FNITC, said: "The collective response
OL,9,Fof the five recognised teaching unions
OL,10,Fwhich comprise the Northern Ireland
OL,11,FTeachers' Council has indicated that
OL,12,Fwe are unable to accept the revised
OL,13,Fpay offer.
OL,15,F"Teachers across the profession, due
OL,16,Fto inadequate funding, resources and
OL,17,Fsupport, feel strongly that they can
OL,18,Fno longer fully meet the needs of
OL,19,Fchildren in their schools, and this
OL,20,Fhas been reflected in their response.
