OL,6,F"It is imperative that we address as a
OL,7,Fmatter of priority the mounting
OL,8,Fpressures being felt in schools.
OL,10,F"UTU remains committed to urgent
OL,11,Fengagement with the employers to seek
OL,12,Fa way forward in the interests of both
OL,13,Fmembers and the children and young
OL,14,Fpeople in their care."
