OL,6,FMark McTaggart, the northern secretary
OL,7,Fwith Irish National Teachers'
OL,8,FOrganisation, added: "Into members
OL,9,Fraised concerns around the clarity of
OL,10,Fthe offer in terms of reducing
OL,11,Fworkload and have indicated that they
OL,12,Fare unable to accept at this time.
OL,14,F"We now seek meaningful engagement
OL,15,Fwith management side which will lead
OL,16,Fto a resolution around the ever-
OL,17,Fincreasing burdens placed on teachers
OL,18,Fand school leaders which will allow
OL,19,Fthem to return to their core role as
OL,20,Feducators of the children and young
OL,21,Fpeople in their care."
