OL,6,FJustin McCamphill, from the NASUWT,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our members have considered the
OL,8,Foffer carefully and have made their
OL,9,Fdecision based on their professional
OL,10,Fjudgement and lived experience in
OL,11,Fschools.
OL,13,F"We recognise the result leaves the
OL,14,Fsituation uncertain. However, we will
OL,15,Fall now seek urgent engagement with
OL,16,Fthe employers and the Department of
OL,17,FEducation to discuss next steps and
OL,18,Fensure teachers' concerns are heard
OL,19,Fand addressed."
