OL,6,FPauline Buchanan, regional secretary
OL,7,Fwith the National Education Union,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Throughout this discussion, our
OL,9,Fmembers have consistently been mindful
OL,10,Fof their commitment to their students.
OL,11,FHowever, over the years, workload,
OL,12,Fbureaucracy, inadequate support and
OL,13,Fdemands on time have increased and
OL,14,Fmust be tackled urgently.
OL,16,F"Management Side must show a genuine
OL,17,Fand good faith commitment to engaging
OL,18,Fwith teachers to address the many
OL,19,Fpressures mounting in schools. We
OL,20,Fremain determined to find a resolution
OL,21,Fand are ready to pursue further talks."
