OL,6,FGraham Gault, NI national secretary at
OL,7,Fthe NIHT, said the union remained
OL,8,Fcommitted to working collectively with
OL,9,Fthe other unions that did not accept
OL,10,Fthe deal.
OL,12,F"While the membership of NAHT voted in
OL,13,Ffavour of accepting the offer, the
OL,14,Fwider NITC position means that the
OL,15,Foffer has not been ratified by all
OL,16,Funions and will, therefore, not be
OL,17,Fprogressed in its current form," he
OL,18,Fsaid.
